metadata.name: A Dance Between Worlds
metadata.description:
"A Dance Between Worlds" is a vibrant and captivating piece of surrealist maximalist art that invites viewers into a realm of dynamic movement and vivid colors. The composition is an explosion of energy and rhythm, filled with an array of dancing figures that seamlessly blend into one another. Each figure possesses its own unique style and form, creating a tapestry of diverse movements and gestures.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI Art show in history, featuring 100 artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
